Name: My Doctor is a Futanari
About the game: Frequent headaches are starting to get in the way of you everyday life. You find a Doctor online, set an appointment and give her a visit. Things take an unexpected turn however, when a simple checkup turns intimate. Will your new GP be able to resolve your qualms? Read through some pretty raunchy(erotic) dialogue, accompanied by spicy nude depictions. Gameplay Kinetic Visual Novel H-Scenes Sexy Voice Acting ~5K words Immerse yourself in the story by typing in your own name, then proceeding to read through a raunchy story from the first-person perspective.
